{"tid":2059373,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"黃家駒58歲生忌　昔日Beyond隊友社交網站發文表達思念","createTime":"2020-06-11T01:06:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T15:45:38.000Z","uid":12558,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"3a1e309d8580efeea1517011abde2b1529dfc645","tid":2059373,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T01:06:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200610/347439923869126656.jpeg/FTRMux-WglGBIpF8bdyU52hAsJGg8cnGj-AveY_gL3k?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200610%2F347439923869126656.jpeg%2FFTRMux-WglGBIpF8bdyU52hAsJGg8cnGj-AveY_gL3k%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=5fb8e124&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日（10/6）是香港殿堂級樂隊Beyond主音黃家駒58歲生忌，昔日隊友一如慣例，紛紛在社交網站貼文與家駒「慶生」，表達對這位Beyond靈魂人物的思念。鼓手葉世榮率先於今日0時0分在微博準時貼文，隨後胞弟黃家強更分別在Facebook及微博貼文紀念哥哥，而結他手黃貫中今早亦在微博表達敬意。"},{"pid":"5ff86c677e3a1449137c0f22d124fde5af0f667a","tid":2059373,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T01:08:23.000Z","msg":"用支博好唔尊重"},{"pid":"4f095bd2a64e17c1fbd290a5ffd134cbc3b462ec","tid":2059373,"uid":244394,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T01:09:28.000Z","msg":"家駒未死會同佢地絕交"},{"pid":"a88f0e2db8a8592e9c23583ff5de515eb1265e6f","tid":2059373,"uid":167658,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T01:22:39.000Z","msg":"家強又要show d figure出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f3b8dde2ba0424b0074eda26cd1f64977173241","tid":2059373,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T01:23:39.000Z","msg":"咁好多fans只係睇到支博係真嘅"},{"pid":"d66bb22e6b2d76fdfa445f0cc198899fb5b58501","tid":2059373,"uid":810,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T01:24:52.000Z","msg":"真人血饅頭"},{"pid":"cdca108e61600b0b739a0b6aceb83b5b08804793","tid":2059373,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy"